Carlito's Way;;91;;82;;R;;A free man after years in prison, Carlito Brigante (Al Pacino) intends to give up his criminal ways, but it's not long before the ex-con is sucked back into the New York City underworld. Reconnecting with his dancer girlfriend, Gail (Penelope Ann Miller), Carlito gets entangled in the shady dealings of his friend Dave Kleinfeld (Sean Penn), who also serves as his lawyer. When Carlito and Kleinfeld run afoul of shifty gangster Benny Blanco (John Alberto Leguizamo), it sets them on a dangerous path.;;Crime,Drama;;Brian De Palma;;1993;;Al Pacino,Sean Penn,Penelope Ann Miller,Luis Guzm√°n,John Leguizamo,Ingrid Rogers,James Rebhorn,Joseph Siravo,Viggo Mortensen,Richard Foronjy,Jorge Porcel,Adrian Pasdar;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/carlitos_way